{"tid":2142300,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"CRE 2020 討論區 (10月香港/12月海外)","createTime":"2020-08-06T10:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T08:02:43.000Z","uid":35677,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ece0d7d6052a909e763e675a142ae97a2301a4d3","tid":2142300,"uid":35677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:18:10.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局發言人今日（八月六日）表示，綜合招聘考試及基本法測試暫定於<span class=\"red\">十月十日及十七日</span>或如有需要於十月內的其他日期在香港舉行，有意應徵學位或專業程度公務員職位的人士<span class=\"red\">可由明日（八月七日）起報名參加</span>。<br />\n<br />\n為方便在香港以外地區升學或居住的考生，是次綜合招聘考試及基本法測試亦暫定於<span class=\"red\">十二月五日</span>在其他七個城市舉行，包括北京、倫敦、三藩市、紐約、多倫多、温哥華及悉尼。於香港以外地區舉行的綜合招聘考試及基本法測試將於本年稍後時間接受申請。<br />\n<br />\n政府今日（八月六日）公布將於九月展開新一輪招聘政務主任、二級行政主任、二級助理貿易主任及二級運輸主任的工作，有意投考人士請報考綜合招聘考試及基本法測試。<br />\n<br />\n科舉2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/recruit/cre/949.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Frecruit%2Fcre%2F949.html&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=8f1a75e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/recruit/cre/949.html</a><br />\n<br />\n6月舊Post:<br />\nCRE 2020 討論區: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1974288\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1974288</a><br />\nCRE 2020 討論區 (2): <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2053376\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2053376</a><br />\nCRE 2020討論區 (3): <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2063215\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2063215</a>"},{"pid":"3a88c0925b83a5a073183615962e79c86b968cbb","tid":2142300,"uid":125670,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T12:21:22.000Z","msg":"10月第1次考cre 可唔可以報埋年尾jre?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c1588f49ea104b84555d732fbceb74365a87cb","tid":2142300,"uid":35677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a88c0925b83a5a073183615962e79c8